  "texts": [
    "We also attempted to iterate on this process using specifically fine-tuned models.",
    "Based on our findings in Sec.",
    "3.3, we observe that most of these publicly available datasets have several limitations.",
    "First, these datasets are often static, synthesized by weak models, limited in scope, and, more importantly, not verified by execution.",
    "Second, these datasets mainly focus on a single type of function-calling category, i.e., outputting a single function call based on the provided tools."
